{
  "stem": "9995.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- you know, it's called Amalia because they were making those pots and pans which were-- had this Amalia, they called, in-- inside and outside.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- later on, when people went to concentration camp, he built barracks over there, and he took those people in them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Incidentally, my husband's cousin and her mother were in Schindler's thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But when later on, when they all had to come to concentration camp, they were, of course, taken off the list.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They survive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The-- his cousin's mother, his aunt, died already.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the cousin is alive over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She's in Israel.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She lives in Netanya.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Easily.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see, Schindler wanted my uncle to be in Amalia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my uncle got a better deal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Since he was working for Hans Frank, he got an apartment in [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was traveling from over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He didn't have to live in ghetto and in camp, so he preferred this.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But were came there so-called what they called action, they took him in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And later on came an order to remove him from the cattle train, and they couldn't find him and his family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Had he gone with Schindler, like Schindler asked him to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, I could have easily gone to Schindler and say, take me, because he knew me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But my mother said we cannot do it because in order to put us on the list, they have to take somebody else off.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's not how we want to survive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
